{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/addtowishlist_gif.gif?t=1730476778\" />Battle Charge is a 3rd person medieval RPG game where you command your troops against the enemy in battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by the cinematic battle scenes of Vikings, The Last Kingdom, Braveheart, Barbarians and others, it is time to have a medieval battle game where you can experience the trilling moments of those army clashes. There will be features like shield wall tactics, traps and ambushes, loyal companions and various types of troops with different weapons and skills. This will help you choose your strategy and tactics in every battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game offers Single player and co-op multiplayer where your friends can play as your companion in the battlefield. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Battle Charge is your gateway to living out the epic scenes that have captivated audiences. Stay tuned for updates. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/line_break_command_your_troops_3.png?t=1730476778\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/shieldwall_command_T.gif?t=1730476778\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/command_charge.gif?t=1730476778\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/charging.gif?t=1730476778\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973420/extras/line_break_realistic_shield_walls_3.png?t=1730476778\" /><img class=\"bb_i